Seq1.CallerContent: I need to schedule an appointment with Dr. Williams. I got disconnected.
Seq1.ReceiverContent: Okay. One moment. Would you like to meet the doctor in person or would you like to make a televisit?

Seq2.ReceiverContent: Okay. One moment. Let me check on the next available slot for you. We do have a slot available on 22nd of December at 11 a.m. Will that be okay with you?

Seq3.ReceiverContent: Before that, one moment. We do have a slot available on 12th of December.

Seq4.ReceiverContent: Yes. At 2 p.m. in the afternoon. Will that be okay with you?

Seq5.ReceiverContent: Okay. One moment. Could I take it? Your date of birth?

Seq6.ReceiverContent: Your last name is Moyer, am I correct?

Seq7.ReceiverContent: And may I know the reason of the appointment?

Seq8.CallerContent: She is 90 years old and she doesn't feel good. She's cold all the time. And she wants to get the RSV shot also.
Seq8.ReceiverContent: Okay. So is this going to be a follow-up?

Seq9.CallerContent: What do you mean a follow-up? No, it's an appointment. I don't understand.
Seq9.ReceiverContent: Okay. Just confirm. I have fixed an appointment on 12th of December at 2 p.m. to meet the doctor in person.

Seq10.ReceiverContent: Is there anything else that I missed?

Seq11.ReceiverContent: Okay. Thank you for calling Crofton Family Practice and you have a great day.
